ai-patthana23.33:0.2_0: under the influence of the Dhamma: the Protector of the Three Worlds
ai-patthana23.33:1.1_0: Not by means of this, they don’t give rise to the skillful teaching.
ai-patthana23.33:2.1_0: Not by those of few wishes, etc., do not give rise to unprofitable thoughts.
ai-patthana23.33:3.1_0: Not attending on the dealings that arise because of extremely undecidedness. It doesn’t give rise to cause or reason.
